<s> It appears in DOM1  </s>
<s> but not in DOM2 or DOM3 WD.  </s>
<s> I see that it exists both in IE6 and in NS6 -  </s>
<s> although it doesn't seem to work on the SVG documents that I have tested it in.  </s>
<s> Has it been removed from the spec?  </s>
<s> If not should it be available on documentElements other than the html element.  </s>
