<s> Thanks in advance, Jonathan.  </s>
<s> It's in DOM2 HTML (not DOM Core).  </s>
<s> And therefore it is not guaranteed to be present for things like SVG.  </s>
<s> Boris 617-864-9910 If you put garbage in a computer nothing comes out but garbage.  </s>
